## 🖥️ How to Run Locally

### Option 1: Python Server (Recommended)
```
cd "c:\Users\gugan\Downloads\skill builder"
python -m http.server 8080
```
Then open **http://localhost:8080/mit_skill_builder_practice.html** in your browser.

### Option 2: VS Code Live Server
1. Install the "Live Server" extension in VS Code
2. Right-click `mit_skill_builder_practice.html` → **Open with Live Server**
3. It auto-opens in your browser

### Option 3: Direct File Open
> [!WARNING]
> This won't work because Skulpt loads from CDN and browsers block scripts on `file://` URLs.

